HEADWORD: Posting
<hw>Post"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act
of traveling post.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bookkeeping)</fld> <def>The act of transferring an
account, as from the journal to the ledger.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Posting house</b></col>, <cd>a post house.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Post-it note</ent>⟦br⟧
